title: 10 Things You Don't Know
overview: Each comedic half-hour self-contained episode will highlight a celebrity and countdown the 10 most unique and surprising facts you don't know about them. From Brad Pitt and Jennifer Lopez to Keanu Reeves, Tiffany Haddish, Lady Gaga and more, the series will uncover all the hysterical, outrageous, only-in-Hollywood scoop that prove stars really are just like us. These facts will get crazier and more unbelievable, ending with the most mind-blowing revelation that will leave even the most hardcore fans saying "WTF!".
